Cost-Effectiveness Analysis of a HMGA2 Prognostic Test for Acute Myeloid 
Leukemia in a Canadian Setting.

Tremblay G(1)(2), Rousseau B(3), Marquis M(4)(5), Beaubois C(4)(5), Sauvageau 
G(4)(5)(6)(7), Hébert J(8)(9)(10)(11).

Author information:
