(2)Geneconomics Inc, 1372 rue Du crépuscule, Lévis, QC, Canada, G7A 4K3. 
gabrielt.ecn@gmail.com.
(3)Adelphi Values, Bollington, UK.
(4)The Leucegene Project, Université de Montréal, Montreal, QC, Canada.
(5)Quebec Leukemia Cell Bank, Research Centre, Maisonneuve-Rosemont Hospital, 
5415 l'Assomption Blvd, Montreal, QC, H1T 2M4, Canada.
(6)Division of Hematology-Oncology, Maisonneuve-Rosemont Hospital, Montreal, QC, 
