(8)The Leucegene Project, Université de Montréal, Montreal, QC, Canada. 
josee.hebert@umontreal.ca.
(9)Quebec Leukemia Cell Bank, Research Centre, Maisonneuve-Rosemont Hospital, 
5415 l'Assomption Blvd, Montreal, QC, H1T 2M4, Canada. 
josee.hebert@umontreal.ca.
(10)Division of Hematology-Oncology, Maisonneuve-Rosemont Hospital, Montreal, 
QC, Canada. josee.hebert@umontreal.ca.
(11)Department of Medicine, Faculty of Medicine, Université de Montréal, 
